{"tid":1340752,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"豬隊友/神助攻？元朗事件只會令政府陷於萬劫不復之地","createTime":"2019-07-21T16:12:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T16:55:08.000Z","uid":264584,"like":68,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"20a48a996e771cae2b64d1fab49aa108489d9912","tid":1340752,"uid":264584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:12:10.000Z","msg":"本身今晚衝擊中聯辦 <br />\n政府同一大堆建制可以出黎講下最嚴厲嘅譴責 <br />\n乘機話運動已經變質<br />\n令到部分市民都覺得過分咗<br />\n<br />\n但元朗事件嘅出現<br />\n令到香港人醒覺 原來政府真係可以無所不用其極<br />\n可以警黑合作得咁無間 置普通市民性命於不顧<br />\n成功又再將焦點擺落政府<br />\n<br />\n而家政府又要龜縮<br />\n因為唔知點處理元朗事件<br />\n如果要譴責 應該譴責邊一邊多啲？<br />\n<br />\n只係譴責示威者 人地冇傷人喎  <br />\n明顯重視西環多過市民&mdash;-》引發民怨<br />\n譴責元朗牛屎佬多啲 又或者譴責示威同一程度？<br />\n又會得罪牛屎佬 同令到中央唔滿意<br />\n<br />\n咁點算？<br />\n我俾個建議啦 <br />\n政府可以係最嚴厲嘅譴責加個真字<br />\n用 真&middot;最嚴厲嘅譴責<br />\n打和！"},{"pid":"1b3dbdaee680f5cf90483cd6408c375c41a82884","tid":1340752,"uid":70650,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:12:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f529db10f2f6c8eca7be65b280737632fdd4394","tid":1340752,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:13:18.000Z","msg":"有人要做CPR<br />\n可能真出事"},{"pid":"b81092c96fd6d7d6225326c12419b20fe84814f7","tid":1340752,"uid":74778,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:14:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">官</span><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">商</span><span style=\"font-size: large;\">鄉</span><span style=\"font-size: small;\">黑</span><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">民</span><br />\n<br />\n點打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9863fefa70c6f94c0df80a25223b3cb3ab49a89","tid":1340752,"uid":264584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T16:14:08.000Z","msg":"呢鋪元朗牛屎佬註定俾人祭旗"},{"pid":"19eaab806ef70dfd9b321ffab937f831ee825c7c","tid":1340752,"uid":279357,"like":0,"disl